1.title: Episode #2.1
1.plot: Why does a bodybuilder who swears that he has GoPro evidence of an accident between the motorcycle he was riding and a tuk-tuk lie to the police? Paris's key passport lands her in some hot water in Ho Chi Minh City. Two amazing twiblings ten years in the making are born four days apart in different countries, but will they get to see each other?

2.title: Episode #2.2
2.plot: Rodney ransacks a mini-bar and refuses to pay up, but he has a bigger problem - his immigration visa has expired. Daniel goes looking for some ping-pong bars with his friends, but finds himself in a critical situation after his tuk-tuk driver takes them to a dodgy strip club and they argue with the bouncers over the admission price. Two Australian brothers wrestle with a group of ladyboys in Phuket, and the bromance backfires.

3.title: Episode #2.3
3.plot: Elle's dreams are shattered when the love of her life falls off a balcony onto a patch of grass. Ilario, a superhero, needs a passport but wants much more. Mickey is on top of the world in Bangkok one moment, and out of control the next.

4.title: Episode #2.4
4.plot: Two boys from Bendigo are out to break all the rules in Phuket, and end up having to face the music. Amourous bride-to-be Angie has all the right moves, but what does she really want? Australian blood is spilt on the streets of Phuket when a sea captain walks around with a knife.

5.title: Episode #2.5
5.plot: Alex came to Phuket to train, but then he did something really crazy - he made a fraudulent insurance claim and lied about it to the police. The twin tub from hell puts love on the rocks when it damages a passport left in a jeans pocket. It's Code Red for Team Embassy as a deadly earthquake strikes Nepal and two Royal Australian Air Force planes bring Australian survivors from Kathmandu to Bangkok.

1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Party girls go wild in Phuket, and now their boyfriends are missing. An anxious young traveller lands in hot water, but there's more to his passport than meets the eye. Two men who are partners have paid thousands for their twins, and now everyone's future hangs in the balance.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Can Aussie Rob get his life back after he falls victim to lies and deception in Thailand's city of sin? The fight to bring baby Laney home pushes Trudy to the edge. What will a mother say after she finds out that her daughter has eloped to the jungles of Chiang Mai?

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Australians are put on high alert after wealthy banker Nathan Hansford goes missing. Bai and Steven have their fairy-tale wedding hijacked by a massive jet ski scam. What went wrong to make Amy's dream holiday come crashing down?

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: An Australian party animal who is busted for drugs in a country where they still have the death penalty has a secret escape plan. A silly mistake with taxis in Bangkok could cost the O'Donoghues their savings. Consular staff rub shoulders with the rich and powerful at the glamour bash of the year. Can the Embassy save a broke and broken-hearted Brian from the Bangkok love rat?

plot: Goes behind the scenes of one of the world's busiest Australian Embassies, in Bangkok, Thailand, following the diplomats that make up Australia's consular team.::Allister Coots
